content:
Some Omni-Channel desktop features aren’t supported in Omni Mobile.

Review these limitations for Omni Mobile.

Omni Mobile supports work from all enhanced channels, except Voice. 
Omni Mobile supports status-based capacity, but not tab-based capacity. See Understand Capacity Models.
Omni Mobile doesn’t automatically accept work requests even if the option is enabled in Service Channel Settings.
Omni Mobile doesn’t support push time-out even if the option is enabled in Routing Configuration Settings.
Omni Mobile doesn’t support Omni Toolkit API.
title: Omni Channel Service Cloud Limitations
